summary: Despite the cold I was able to do some more additional work to my draft for this painting I am planning. I made these miniature...
caption:
Despite the cold I was able to do some more additional work to my draft for this painting I am planning. I made these miniature sculpey macaroni so I could photoshop it in there. The begonia at work is looking really great too so I decided to use that instead of a palm plant.

Also, the talented @bonnini has been giving me arches ideas with her architectural paintings and drawings, if you love that kind of work, please go look at her instagram.

blog.description:
All the photographs posted here are original work from photographers I follow  on tumblr . My aim is  twofold, share the inspiration, and give photographers a bit more exposure .     
 I am also part of the  Lux Lit  team of rebloggers, and ms-excuse me with Thierry Facon, where the main focus is to bring you lesser known photographs that we feel deserve some more attention. 
 Please feel free to contact me if you have any questions or comments, or would  like me to check out your blog;  I'm on a constant quest for new photography blogs to follow .

summary: you know what sucks? I am almost finished with Shay, could have finished him today but nooooo It had to be really dark and rainy...
body:
you know what sucks? I am almost finished with Shay, could have finished him today but nooooo It had to be really dark and rainy all day.

Dont get me wrong i love stormy weather but man. I paint next to a window so its my best light source. Terrible lighting in my apartment. Hopefully I can get him finished tomorrow. I want to show him off Monday. XD
